
environment command:
1.python 3.x
2.pip install --> requests[socks] lxml beautifulsoup4
3.You must be login pixiv with your account, This crawler use shadowsocks


Usage:

1. download all illustrators.
   python get_illustrator.py all

2. download user defined illustrator.
   python get_illustrator.py illustrator 20980424

3. download update all bookmask illustrators picture since user defined date.
   python get_illustrator.py update 20190601
